      "content_html": "\u003ch2\u003eNavigation\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API\"\u003eUnreal Engine C++ API Reference\u003c/a\u003e \u003e \u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins\"\u003ePlugins\u003c/a\u003e \u003e \u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/ScriptableToolsFramework\"\u003eScriptableToolsFramework\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eClasses\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003ctable\u003e\n  \u003cthead\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003e \u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003eType\u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003eName\u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003eDescription\u003c/th\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/thead\u003e\n  \u003ctbody\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/4dffe638-fdd6-4f42-b429-65431ebba246/api_class_public.png\" alt=\"Public class\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Public class\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/4c4e1db0-d04e-44a4-a986-b024bdca3156/api_class_meta.png\" alt=\"UClass\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"UClass\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/ScriptableToolsFramework/BaseTools/UScriptableClickDragTool\"\u003eUScriptableClickDragTool\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/ScriptableToolsFramework/BaseTools/UScriptableClickDragTool\"\u003eUScriptableClickDragTool\u003c/a\u003e is an extension of \u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/ScriptableToolsFramework/UScriptableInteractiveTool\"\u003eUScriptableInteractiveTool\u003c/a\u003e that supports a \"click-drag\" interaction, ie capture the input device on press-down and collect any device movement events until release.\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e \u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/01244ebe-a080-4578-b398-562397dc8462/api_class_public.png\" alt=\"Public class\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Public class\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/9819e1cc-55e8-407c-84e7-6d1ab14b9d2d/api_class_meta.png\" alt=\"UClass\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"UClass\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/ScriptableToolsFramework/BaseTools/UScriptableModularBehaviorTool\"\u003eUScriptableModularBehaviorTool\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eA Scriptable tool base blueprint class which provides support for user defined mouse interaction behaviors\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e \u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/68e14d6d-dc30-43f5-bbf6-319b82edd258/api_class_public.png\" alt=\"Public class\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Public class\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/7aabb1fd-e3f8-4899-8874-cae81db1f4c0/api_class_meta.png\" alt=\"UClass\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"UClass\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/3df4300a-13a2-45cc-8039-160f634fcd3b/api_class_meta_other.png\" alt=\"hidden\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"hidden\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/ScriptableToolsFramework/BaseTools/UScriptableSingleClickTool\"\u003eUScriptableSingleClickTool\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/ScriptableToolsFramework/BaseTools/UScriptableSingleClickTool\"\u003eUScriptableSingleClickTool\u003c/a\u003e is an extension of \u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/ScriptableToolsFramework/UScriptableInteractiveTool\"\u003eUScriptableInteractiveTool\u003c/a\u003e that supports a \"click\" interaction, ie button press-down-and-release on an arbitrary Target (defined by the Tool).\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e \u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/tbody\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n",
